quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  12,7,"Ni$, di Yusef akked watma s, illa ussekni i wid isteqsayen"
  12,8,"Mi nnan: \"war ccekk, ifen a$, Yusef akked gma s, akken iten iĂȘemmel babat nne$, u nekwni d ĂźĂźeĂŽma. Babat nne$, s tidep, haat di ttelfan n Ă»Ă»eĂȘ"
  12,9,"En$et Yusef, ne$ nfut ep si tmurt, a d ilhu degwen babat wen, sinna, a ppu$alem d imdanen ixeddmen ayen ilhan"
  12,10,"Inna win d immeslayen, degsen: \"ur neqqet Yusef, veggĂŽet ep ar lqaĂąa n wannu. Ma tgam akka, a t iddem yiwen umsebrid"
  12,11,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, acu k iu$en, ur a$ tuminev ara, $ef Yusef. Nekwni, fellas, s tidep, d unĂ»iĂȘen"
  12,12,"Sseddu t yidne$ azekka, ad izhu, ad iurar. Nekwni, war ccekk, a nĂȘareb fellas"
  12,13,"Inna: \"nek, s tidep, $weble$ ma tebbwim t yidwen, ugade$ a t iĂ§Ă§ lweĂȘc, kunwi testehzam degs"
  12,14,"Nnan: \"ma iĂ§Ă§a t lweĂȘc, u nekwni d ĂźĂźeĂŽma, s tidep a nili d imexsuĂŽen"
  12,15,"Mi t bbwin, mwafaqen a t rĂŽen ar lqaĂąa n wannu, NweĂȘĂȘa yas: \"ad asen temlev, s tidep, lameĂŽ agi nnsen, nitni ur Ă©ĂŽin"
  12,16,"U$alen d tameddit, ar babat sen, pprun"
  12,17,"Nnan: \"a babat nne$, s tidep, nĂŽuĂȘ a nemzizzel, neooa Yusef ar lqecc nne$, iĂ§Ă§a t lweĂȘc. Ur a$ teppamnev, xas nenna d tidep"
  12,18,"Bbwin d tasedrit is, degs idamen n rrya. Inna: \"xaĂźi! D iman nnwen i wen d iccacven lameĂŽ. Ilha Ă»Ă»beĂŽ. Anuju $eĂŽ Ăebbi, mgal ayen d teĂȘkam"
  12,19,"Usan d iminigen, uznen win id ippagwmen, issader ssvel is. Inna: \"a lxiĂŽ, wagi d aqcic\"! Ffren t, amzun d sselĂąa. Ăebbi IĂ©ĂŽa acu xeddmen"
  12,20,"Zzenzen t, s ĂŽĂŽxa, s kra iĂ»uĂŽdiyen. Ur as fkin ara azal"
  12,21,"Inna, i tmeĂźĂźut is, UmaĂ»ĂŽi i t iu$en: \"eĂŽĂȘeb yis, amar ad a$ infaĂą, at nerr d mmit nne$\". Akka ay NesseqĂąad Yusef di tmurt, iwakken ad as NesseĂȘfev asefru n temsal. Ăebbi d Amezwaru s lameĂŽ iS, maca tegwti n medden ur Ă©ĂŽin ara"
  12,22,"Mi d immeĂȘtel, Nefka yas Ă»Ă»wab, tussna. Akka ay Nepkafi iĂąaĂŽviyen"
  12,23,"Teb$a t tin u$ur izde$. Terra tibbura, u tenna: \"eyya keĂ§Ă§\"! Inna: \"ad iyi Ineooi Ăebbi! Ni$ bab iw iĂŽĂȘeb yissi. S tidep, ur rebĂȘen imednas"
  12,24,"S tidep, teb$a t, u neppa ib$a p, lemmer ur iwala ara atebbet n Mass is. Akka, iwakken a NessebĂąad fellas tuccva, lĂąaĂŽ. Neppa, s tidep, seg imdanen nneÂŁ izedganen"
  12,25,"Uzzlen ar tebburt, tcerreg as tasedrit is, si zdeffir. Mmugren, argaz is, ar tebburt. Tenna: \"acu ay d aqeĂźĂźi n win iĂąabwlen ad iccmet tawacult ik, siwa lĂȘebs ne$ aĂąaqeb aqeĂŽĂȘan"
  12,26,"Inna: \"d neppat iyi ib$an\". Icuhhed ed yiwen unagi si twacult is: \"ma teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdat, tenna d tidep, u neppa d akeddab"
  12,27,"Ma teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdeffir, teskaddeb, u neppa seg at tidep"
  12,28,"Mi iwala teqqeĂŽs tsedrit si zdeffir, inna: \"ayagi, war ccekk, si nncub nnkwent. Ih, nncub nnkwent d timeqwĂŽaĂȘanin"
  12,29,"A Yusef, ppu ayagi, u kem ssuter ssmaĂȘ ubekkav im. Kem, s tidep, teccvev"